ly to have assembled, in its entirety, through the\ndisruption of dwarf galaxies similar to the low-luminosity dSphs studied here.\n(ABRIDGED).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Sep 2000 21:53:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-08-23"}
